# Theme Token Enforcement

Every color, spacing, typography, and border-radius value MUST use Pebble theme tokens. Never hardcode.

## Forbidden Patterns

```typescript
// ❌ Hardcoded colors
backgroundColor: 'white'
backgroundColor: '#ffffff'
color: '#000000'
color: 'black'
color: 'red'
borderColor: '#e0e0e0'

// ❌ Hardcoded spacing
padding: '16px'
margin: '24px'
gap: '8px'

// ❌ Hardcoded typography
fontSize: '14px'
fontWeight: 600
lineHeight: '20px'

// ❌ Hardcoded border radius
borderRadius: '8px'
borderRadius: '50%'
```

## Required Patterns

```typescript
// ✅ Theme colors
backgroundColor: theme.colorSurface
color: theme.colorOnSurface
borderColor: theme.colorOutlineVariant

// ✅ Theme spacing
padding: theme.space400          // 16px
margin: theme.space600           // 24px
gap: theme.space200              // 8px

// ✅ Theme typography (use V2 tokens)
${theme.typestyleV2BodyMedium}   // 14px body text
${theme.typestyleV2TitleLarge}   // 22px section heading

// ✅ Theme shape
borderRadius: theme.shapeCornerLg   // 8px
borderRadius: theme.shapeCornerFull // pill shape
```

## Common Token Mappings

| Hardcoded | Token |
|-----------|-------|
| `'white'` / `'#fff'` | `theme.colorSurface` or `theme.colorSurfaceBright` |
| `'black'` / `'#000'` | `theme.colorOnSurface` |
| `'#666'` / `'gray'` | `theme.colorOnSurfaceVariant` |
| `'16px'` padding | `theme.space400` |
| `'24px'` padding | `theme.space600` |
| `'8px'` gap | `theme.space200` |
| `'8px'` radius | `theme.shapeCornerLg` |
| `'12px'` radius | `theme.shapeCorner2xl` |

## Exceptions

- Third-party library configuration that requires literal values
- CSS custom properties / keyframe animations using `calc()` with token values
- SVG attributes that cannot accept token values
